{"image_id": "VRSN_2007_page_139", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "VERISIGN, INC. AND SUBSIDIARIES", "bbox": [439.4, 140.2, 798.7, 161.0]}, {"text": "NOTES TO CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS—(Continued)", "bbox": [279.5, 177.7, 958.7, 198.5]}, {"text": "DECEMBER 31, 2007, 2006 AND 2005", "bbox": [445.2, 215.2, 792.7, 236.0]}, {"text": "Agreement, PayPal acquired certain assets related to VeriSign’s Payment Gateway business and assumed certain", "bbox": [143.8, 265.4, 1085.3, 286.3]}, {"text": "liabilities related thereto for $370 million in cash. The Payment Gateway business was part of the Internet", "bbox": [143.8, 290.4, 1028.1, 311.3]}, {"text": "Services Group segment.", "bbox": [143.8, 315.4, 352.9, 336.3]}, {"text": "In connection with the sale of the Payment Gateway business, the Company entered into a Transitional", "bbox": [185.5, 363.3, 1044.4, 384.1]}, {"text": "Service Agreement (“TSA”) with PayPal to provide certain transitional network and customer support services.", "bbox": [143.8, 388.3, 1074.8, 409.1]}, {"text": "The related fees were recorded as a direct reduction to the respective costs and expenses included in discontinued", "bbox": [143.8, 413.3, 1090.6, 434.1]}, {"text": "operations. The expected cash flows under the TSA did not represent a significant continuation of the direct cash", "bbox": [143.8, 438.3, 1086.5, 459.1]}, {"text": "flows of the disposed payment gateway business. In April 2006, PayPal elected to terminate the customer support", "bbox": [143.8, 463.3, 1092.3, 484.1]}, {"text": "services provided by VeriSign under the TSA. In September 2006, PayPal elected to terminate the billing", "bbox": [143.8, 488.3, 1023.2, 509.2]}, {"text": "services, production services and other transitional services provided under the TSA.", "bbox": [143.8, 513.3, 852.5, 534.2]}, {"text": "The following table presents the calculation of the gain on the sale of the Payment Gateway business:", "bbox": [185.5, 561.2, 1033.1, 582.0]}, {"