ox": [185.5, 1278.3, 391.8, 1299.2]}, {"text": "In January 2007, VeriSign initiated a restructuring plan to execute a company-wide reorganization replacing", "bbox": [185.5, 1314.9, 1089.9, 1335.8]}, {"text": "the previous business unit structure with a new combined worldwide sales and services team, and an integrated", "bbox": [143.8, 1339.9, 1070.7, 1360.8]}, {"text": "development and products organization. The restructuring plan included workforce reductions, abandonment of", "bbox": [143.8, 1364.9, 1075.5, 1385.8]}, {"text": "excess facilities, and other exit costs. To date, VeriSign has recorded $29.6 million in restructuring charges under", "bbox": [143.8, 1389.9, 1091.4, 1410.8]}, {"text": "its 2007 restructuring plan.", "bbox": [143.8, 1415.0, 368.8, 1435.8]}, {"text": "Š", "bbox": [1173.9, 492.4, 1198.9, 506.3]}, {"text": "131", "bbox": [603.4, 1465.8, 634.6, 1486.6]}, {"text": "Form 10-K", "bbox": [1174.6, 362.4, 1199.6, 481.3]}]}